# What NOT to upload to Cloud Build for `gcloud run deploy --source .`.
# The container image (see Dockerfile) only needs `packages/`, `apps/` and the
# root workspace files — exclude everything else so the upload is small and the
# build doesn't choke on non-container artifacts (e.g. Tuist/Xcode build output).
#
# Note: a `.gcloudignore` DISABLES gcloud's default .gitignore fallback, so this
# list is authoritative — keep the build inputs above included.
.git/
.github/
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.build/
**/.wrangler/

# Non-container members of the monorepo.
examples/
swift/
docs/
e2e/
extensions/

# Local/dev cruft.
*.log
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
